  - m_Id: 1
    m_Localized: "Straypups\xB4s new album is sooooo meh...."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2
    m_Localized: "Why are Taylor Swim\xB4s tickets sooo crazy expensive, I am gonna
      be broke!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3
    m_Localized: Who even is Bite Direction?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4
    m_Localized: Unpopular opinion but Fin Sheeran has not made a single bad album,
      fight me
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5
    m_Localized: Cardi Sea really said I am going to be the loudest creature in the
      water and never apologized for it
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6
    m_Localized: The ocean at 3am hits different, trust me on this
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7
    m_Localized: Forgot my headphones how am I gonna survive the day??!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8
    m_Localized: Sharks that talk during concerts deserve to be left out in the open
      water!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9
    m_Localized: Bad Guppy really said let me switch languages mid song and still
